&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What Makes Us Unique&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;br&gt;At Cloudbeds, we&#39;re not just building software, we’re transforming hospitality. Our intelligently designed platform powers properties across 150 countries, processing billions in bookings annually. From independent properties to hotel groups, we help hoteliers transform operations and uplevel their commercial strategy through a unified platform that integrates with hundreds of partners. And we do it with a completely remote team. Imagine working alongside global innovators to build AI-powered solutions that solve hoteliers&#39; biggest challenges. Since our founding in 2012, we&#39;ve become the World&#39;s Best Hotel PMS Solutions Provider and landed on Deloitte&#39;s Technology Fast 500 again in 2024, but we&#39;re just getting started.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a highly organized, proactive, detail-oriented, and collaborative &lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(38, 28, 10);&quot;&gt;Regional HR &amp;amp; People Operations Specialist&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;to support our growing People organization across the United States and Canada.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role will serve as a critical operational partner supporting:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;NORAM HRBPs;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;People Operations;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Managers;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;and team members across the region.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ideal candidate thrives in a fast-paced, highly collaborative, globally distributed environment and enjoys balancing operational execution, employee support, compliance coordination, HR systems administration, process improvement, and cross-functional partnership.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role is instrumental in helping ensure smooth employee lifecycle management, strong operational execution, leave administration, HR compliance, and an exceptional team member experience throughout the NORAM region.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is an excellent opportunity for someone looking to deepen their experience in regional HR.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(38, 28, 10);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Our People Team&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We’re a globally distributed, multicultural People Team spanning North America, Latin America, EMEA, and APAC, and that global footprint isn’t just a fact; it’s a strength we fully embrace. Our team brings a rich blend of perspectives, experiences, and cultural fluency that fuels everything we do, from nuanced people strategies to inclusive systems and scalable processes that work for everyone, everywhere.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We collaborate with heart and hustle. Despite time zones and borders, we operate with high trust, clear communication, and deep mutual respect. Whether we’re partnering with hiring managers, leading HR transformation, supporting regional teams, or crafting intentional team member experiences, we show up for each other and for the people we serve!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a team where empathy meets execution. Where people who thrive are those who are curious, proactive, globally minded, and genuinely passionate about making Cloudbeds a place where every team member can do their best work. We’re not just People Team, we’re culture shapers, problem solvers, strategy supporters, and people-first builders.&lt;/p&gt;
